</code></pre></div></div>
<p>enable httpd firewall</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>firewall-cmd --permanent --zone=public --add-service=http 
firewall-cmd --permanent --zone=public --add-service=https
firewall-cmd --reload
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>install remi php</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>rpm -Uvh http://rpms.remirepo.net/enterprise/remi-release-7.rpm
yum -y install yum-utils
yum update
</code></pre></div></div>

